<content>
    <para id="id14506753">
      <emphasis effect="bold">AE_Tutorial 12. Problems on OSCILLATORS</emphasis>
    </para>
    <para id="id14282581">Problems have been taken from:</para>
    <para id="id14282585">“Microelectronic Circuit Design” by R.C.Jaeger and T.N. Blalock, 2<sup>nd</sup> Edition, McGraw Hill,2006.</para>
    <para id="id14767955">“Microelectronic Circuits- Analysis &amp; Design”, Muhammad H. Rashid, Thomson, Indian Edition, 1999.</para>
    <para id="id5720659">
      <emphasis effect="italics">Problem (1)Wien Bridge Oscillator</emphasis>
    </para>
    <figure id="id14519860">
      <media id="id14519860_media" alt="">
        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/Picture 1-570a.png" id="id14519860__onlineimage" height="471" width="649"/>
      </media>
    </figure>
    <figure id="id14510179">
      <media id="id14510179_media" alt="">
        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics1-9d3d.png" id="id14510179__onlineimage" height="61" width="370"/>
      </media>
