        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics17-4a79.png" id="id13244365__onlineimage" height="26" width="490"/>
      </media>
    </figure>
    <para id="id14766681">Calculate (i) Frequency of oscillation.</para>
    <para id="id14531366">(ii)Check the Barkhausen criteria.</para>
    <para id="id14410569">(iii)Determine R<sub>2</sub>.</para>
    <para id="id14306734">Solution:-</para>
    <para id="id14306739">RFC acts as a open circuit And C<sub>B</sub> and C<sub>E</sub> acts as a short circuit.</para>
    <para id="id14434500">Therefore the Equivalent Circuit is :-</para>
    <para id="id14434504">
      <figure id="id14766510">
