    <para id="id14611107">(i)This <figure id="id5720483"><media id="id5720483_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics29-37a5.png" id="id5720483__onlineimage" height="26" width="23"/></media></figure> can be provided by BJT hence Barkhausen Criteria is satisfied</para>
    <para id="id14520310">(ii)Frequency of oscillation=<figure id="id14520314"><media id="id14520314_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics30-dc2f.png" id="id14520314__onlineimage" height="45" width="192"/></media></figure></para>
