    <para id="id14585685">Design an oscillator at <figure id="id14585689"><media id="id14585689_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics34-49c0.png" id="id14585689__onlineimage" height="32" width="360"/></media></figure></para>
