    <para id="id14538976">Step(1) Choose a suitable value of C:</para>
    <para id="id14538981">Let C=0.01μF</para>
    <para id="id14538985">Step(2) Calculate the value of L from <figure id="id14365263"><media id="id14365263_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics43-85ac.png" id="id14365263__onlineimage" height="33" width="63"/></media></figure></para>
