    <para id="id14528773">Effective Capacitance C<sub>eq</sub> is parallel with <figure id="id10785332"><media id="id10785332_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics61-d496.png" id="id10785332__onlineimage" height="24" width="16"/></media></figure>is given by</para>
    <figure id="id14711474">
