        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics63-5420.png" id="id14472603__onlineimage" height="50" width="528"/>
      </media>
    </figure>
    <para id="id14543368">It is given that 2MHz crystal is used. Hence the result is self consistent.</para>
    <para id="id14543373">This is the frequency of the Crystal Oscillator.</para>
